overview: This series explores the inner workings of the sexual elite. Featured cover girl Teanna Trump is an influencer desperate to break through to a broader audience. Her new photographer can take her there, but if the shoot leaves her feeling aroused then is there something she can do for him? Rounding out the roster are club newcomers Jia Lissa, Baby Nicols, Kenna James, and Eliza Ibarra.
title: Club VXN 8
